window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>One great series at a single offering. </p> <p>She summoned him to a desperate world.</p> <p>Pulled from a mundane life by a beautiful stranger, Michael is offered what he’s always wanted: something to believe in, to care about, to fight for. But he’s no warrior.</p> <p>The people of Vendira have been oppressed by dark magic for centuries, any spark of resistance long since extinguished. They need a symbol of hope to push back against the malevolent forces that rule the world. Could he be what this world so desperately needs?</p> <p>At home, he has always felt unremarkable, easily fading into the background. But here, Michael isn’t special for what he has; he’s special for what he lacks: he is Brandless.</p>"; 
